Improve server stability and resource management for video processing

Introduce `start_server.py` for controlled gunicorn startup, adjust logging levels, optimize memory management with `gc.set_threshold`, reduce thread stack size, fine-tune gunicorn worker counts and timeouts, and add `psutil` for process management and cleanup.

